extends AeImplTraversingVisitor
implements IAeImplVisitor, IAeImplStateNames

Convenience base class for visitors that restore state in implementation objects.

restoreScopeInstance

protected AeActivityScopeImpl restoreScopeInstance(java.lang.String aScopeLocation,
                                                   boolean aGenerateNewObjectIdsFlag)
                                            throws AeBusinessProcessException
Restores the scope instance specified by the path. This path must point to a scope nested within a dynamic scope parent (parallel forEach, onEvent, onAlarm).

Parameters:
aScopeLocation -
aGenerateNewObjectIdsFlag - True if the scope being restored should create new object ids for its child objects. False if the restored scope will be immediately visited and have its object id's restored from the state doc.
Throws:
AeBusinessProcessException
